{"title":"在CentOS上安装Nginx 相关操作","uid":"aa4e9698da0c12599ca77b93ebd8a596","slug":"nginx/ng1","date":"2023-10-16T10:02:22.000Z","updated":"2023-10-16T10:21:13.140Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/nginx/ng1.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<h2 id=\"要在CentOS上安装Nginx，请按照以下步骤进行操作：\"><a href=\"#要在CentOS上安装Nginx，请按照以下步骤进行操作：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"要在CentOS上安装Nginx，请按照以下步骤进行操作：\"></a>要在CentOS上安装Nginx，请按照以下步骤进行操作：</h2><p>1.更新系统软件包：<br>2.安装EPEL存储库（Extra Packages for Enterprise Linux）<br>3.安装Nginx：<br>4.启动Nginx服务：<br>5.设置Nginx开机启动：<br>6.检查Nginx是否正常运行：<br>7.在Web浏览器中输入服务器的IP地址，你应该能够看到Nginx的欢迎页面。<br>8.启动 nginx 成功之后通过 IP 访问失败</p>\n<div class=\"language-bash\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">bash</span><pre class=\"shiki material-theme-palenight\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">1.sudo</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">yum</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">update</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">2.sudo</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">yum</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">install</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">epel-release</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">3.sudo</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">yum</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">install</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">nginx</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">4.sudo</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">systemctl</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">start</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">nginx</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">5.sudo</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">systemctl</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">enable</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">nginx</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">6.sudo</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">systemctl</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">status</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">nginx</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">7.</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">8.systemctl</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">status</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">firewalld.service</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">systemctl</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">stop</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">firewalld.service</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">$</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">nginx常用基础命令</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">netstat</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">-ntlp</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #676E95; font-style: italic\">#查看端口占用</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #676E95; font-style: italic\">#停止</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">/usr/local/nginx/sbin/nginx</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">-s</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">stop/quit</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #676E95; font-style: italic\">#重新加载</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">/usr/local/nginx/sbin/nginx</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">-s</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">reload</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #676E95; font-style: italic\">#修改配置</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">/usr/local/nginx/conf/nginx.conf</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">nginx</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">-c</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">/home/xx/nginx.conf</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #676E95; font-style: italic\">#-c &lt;/path/to/config&gt; 为 Nginx 指定一个配置文件，来代替缺省的。 </span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #676E95; font-style: italic\">#例如：nginx -t -c /usr/local/nginx/conf/nginx.conf 判断配置文件是否正确</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">nginx</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">-t</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">nginx</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">-v</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #676E95; font-style: italic\">#建议一次性安装以下四个依赖库：pcre、zlib、OpenSSL和gd-devel</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #FFCB6B\">yum</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">-y</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">install</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">pcre</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">pcre-devel</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">zlib</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">zlib-devel</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">openssl</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">openssl-devel</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">gd</span><span style=\"color: #BABED8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C3E88D\">gd-devel</span></span></code></pre></div>","feature":true,"text":"要在CentOS上安装Nginx，请按照以下步骤进行操作：1.更新系统软件包：2.安装EPEL存储库（Extra Packages for Enterprise...","permalink":"/post/nginx/ng1","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":896,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Nginx","slug":"Nginx","count":2,"path":"api/categories/Nginx.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"nginx命令","slug":"nginx命令","count":2,"path":"api/tags/nginx命令.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%A6%81%E5%9C%A8CentOS%E4%B8%8A%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85Nginx%EF%BC%8C%E8%AF%B7%E6%8C%89%E7%85%A7%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%8B%E6%AD%A5%E9%AA%A4%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%EF%BC%9A\"><span class=\"toc-text\">要在CentOS上安装Nginx，请按照以下步骤进行操作：</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"吾曜","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/126133433?v=4","link":"/","description":"人生不过如此，且行且珍惜，所有的磨难都是生命的财富。","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"hidden":false,"prev_post":{"title":"Nginx前端静态项目部署","uid":"6edc7e80b6c423be10ef2818f163d62f","slug":"nginx/ng2","date":"2023-10-17T18:02:22.000Z","updated":"2023-12-13T09:04:35.439Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/nginx/ng2.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/126133433?v=4","text":"Nginx 可以部署以下几类不同类型的项目：静态网站：